00:15:33,320 --> 00:15:34,999
I just wanted to explain

293
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:36,830
why I switched sides this afternoon.

294
00:15:58,000 --> 00:15:59,172
Don't look.

295
00:15:59,914 --> 00:16:00,990
I want to look.

296
00:16:04,360 --> 00:16:05,790
Why can't I look?

297
00:16:07,800 --> 00:16:09,830
Oh, I really didn't expect

298
00:16:10,040 --> 00:16:12,524
Mr. Siyan went out late at night

299
00:16:12,525 --> 00:16:14,590
just to do something like this.

300
00:16:15,440 --> 00:16:17,630
We're just doing physical training.

301
00:16:17,880 --> 00:16:19,919
That's what I meant too.

302
00:16:19,920 --> 00:16:20,870
What?

303
00:16:20,960 --> 00:16:22,270
What did you think I meant?

304
00:16:23,600 --> 00:16:24,350
Nothing.

305
00:16:25,720 --> 00:16:26,710
I'll stop messing around.

306
00:16:27,400 --> 00:16:28,870
This is a flight academy.

307
00:16:29,320 --> 00:16:30,550
You want to be a pilot?

308
00:16:32,360 --> 00:16:33,230
Yes.

309
00:16:33,520 --> 00:16:34,790
So

310
00:16:35,400 --> 00:16:37,270
you never cared for business.

311
00:16:37,388 --> 00:16:40,390
You've acted like a spoiled heir

312
00:16:40,440 --> 00:16:42,350
just to disappoint Father and Mother.

313
00:16:43,280 --> 00:16:45,270
You wanted to marry me

314
00:16:45,280 --> 00:16:46,879
just to annoy them

315
00:16:46,880 --> 00:16:49,070
so that they'd kick you
out of the Lu family.

316
00:16:49,200 --> 00:16:49,959
Then,

317
00:16:49,960 --> 00:16:52,279
you could focus on learning to fly.

318
00:16:52,280 --> 00:16:53,258
Is that so?

319
00:16:54,285 --> 00:16:55,110
Yes.

320
00:16:57,280 --> 00:16:58,910
Kid.

321
00:16:58,960 --> 00:17:00,750
It's a pity you're not an actor.

322
00:17:01,891 --> 00:17:03,487
Now you know everything.

323
00:17:05,440 --> 00:17:06,950
Can you keep my secret?

324
00:17:09,360 --> 00:17:10,519
Call me Sister.

325
00:17:10,520 --> 00:17:11,990
And I'll think about it.

326
00:17:13,520 --> 00:17:15,550
Lin Chuning, is that necessary?

327
00:17:16,840 --> 00:17:19,190
I'll tell Father and Mother then.

328
00:17:19,560 --> 00:17:20,359
Later,

329
00:17:20,360 --> 00:17:21,919
if they lock you in your room,

330
00:17:21,920 --> 00:17:23,656
don't go begging me.

331
00:17:23,657 --> 00:17:25,799
♪Waiting endlessly♪

332
00:17:25,800 --> 00:17:28,204
♪You're the moon above the treetops♪

333
00:17:28,205 --> 00:17:29,058
Sister.

334
00:17:29,760 --> 00:17:30,750
Mm.

335
00:17:30,800 --> 00:17:31,670
Good boy.

336
00:17:31,880 --> 00:17:32,835
Keep it a secret.

337
00:17:34,160 --> 00:17:36,364
I said I'll think about it.

338
00:17:36,365 --> 00:17:38,599
♪My longing haunts my heart♪

339
00:17:38,600 --> 00:17:40,239
Lin Chuning, you're cheating.

340
00:17:40,240 --> 00:17:41,190
I'm not.

341
00:17:41,840 --> 00:17:42,919
Lin Chuning.

342
00:17:42,920 --> 00:17:44,199
Call me Sister.

343
00:17:44,200 --> 00:17:45,176
Lin Chuning.

344
00:17:45,177 --> 00:17:46,770
(Lu Residence)

345
00:17:58,280 --> 00:17:59,990
Have you thought it through?

346
00:18:08,080 --> 00:18:09,630
Come down and talk.

347
00:18:18,885 --> 00:18:19,870
Speak.

348
00:18:22,000 --> 00:18:23,390
That's your attitude?

349
00:18:24,474 --> 00:18:25,667
So have you decided?

350
00:18:25,668 --> 00:18:26,710
Sister.

351
00:18:28,800 --> 00:18:30,710
I'll keep your secret

352
00:18:31,000 --> 00:18:32,510
if you promise me something.

353
00:18:34,120 --> 00:18:35,510
What is it?

354
00:18:35,640 --> 00:18:38,119
Xiaorou was forced to have an abortion

355
00:18:38,120 --> 00:18:39,910
and died in my arms.

356
00:18:40,240 --> 00:18:41,599
Mr. Gao once promised

357
00:18:41,600 --> 00:18:43,110
to give her a proper burial.

358
00:18:43,440 --> 00:18:44,519
I went to see it,

359
00:18:44,520 --> 00:18:45,399
but the grave

360
00:18:45,400 --> 00:18:46,630
was completely empty.

361
00:18:46,960 --> 00:18:48,110
Xiaorou

362
00:18:48,400 --> 00:18:49,390
is alive.

363
00:18:49,520 --> 00:18:50,750
You guessed right.

364
00:18:51,040 --> 00:18:52,879
So I need your help rescuing Xiaorou

365
00:18:52,880 --> 00:18:54,670
and bringing Mr. Gao to justice.

366
00:18:56,560 --> 00:18:57,390
Deal.

367
00:18:57,760 --> 00:18:58,470
Nice.

368
00:18:59,360 --> 00:19:00,150
Pinky swear.

369
00:19:35,000 --> 00:19:36,279
You're aware of danger,

370
00:19:36,280 --> 00:19:37,510
but your reflexes need work.

371
00:19:37,920 --> 00:19:38,959
What are you doing?

372
00:19:38,960 --> 00:19:40,870
Lu Residence is full of danger.

373
00:19:41,137 --> 00:19:42,473
I can't always be by your side.

374
00:19:42,474 --> 00:19:44,658
You need self-defense skills.

375
00:19:46,240 --> 00:19:46,950
Sure.

376
00:19:47,502 --> 00:19:49,132
Sure? Break free.

377
00:19:52,428 --> 00:19:53,479
See?

378
00:19:53,480 --> 00:19:54,990
Men are far stronger.

379
00:19:55,360 --> 00:19:57,030
When you lack strength,

380
00:19:57,200 --> 00:19:58,470
try something else.

381
00:19:59,640 --> 00:20:00,292
Come on.

382
00:20:01,240 --> 00:20:02,070
Same move.

383
00:20:02,120 --> 00:20:03,081
Grab me.

384
00:20:04,680 --> 00:20:07,470
If someone grabs your hands from behind,

385
00:20:07,920 --> 00:20:09,750
try using your head to hit him first.

386
00:20:10,154 --> 00:20:11,510
When he feels pain,

387
00:20:11,754 --> 00:20:13,338
twist the wrist

388
00:20:13,674 --> 00:20:15,035
and turn around.

389
00:20:25,960 --> 00:20:26,990
Ms. Chuning.

390
00:20:27,171 --> 00:20:28,460
Master asked me to inform you

391
00:20:28,460 --> 00:20:30,559
that tomorrow is perfect
for acknowledging your ancestry.

392
00:20:30,560 --> 00:20:32,430
Got it.

393
00:20:43,980 --> 00:20:46,039
(Lu Ancestral Shrine)

394
00:20:46,040 --> 00:20:47,359
Today, Lu's daughter

395
00:20:47,360 --> 00:20:48,830
returns to her bloodline.

396
00:20:49,040 --> 00:20:50,639
Strong fire banishes disaster,

397
00:20:50,640 --> 00:20:52,510
and fortune shall follow.

398
00:20:55,320 --> 00:20:56,110
Step forward.

399
00:21:18,422 --> 00:21:19,761
(Lu Siyan.)

400
00:21:20,468 --> 00:21:21,790
(From this day on,)

401
00:21:22,468 --> 00:21:25,150
(she can only be your older sister.)

402
00:21:46,028 --> 00:21:48,498
Why did the doors close?

403
00:21:51,880 --> 00:21:55,030
Mr. Lu, this isn't a good omen.

404
00:21:55,400 --> 00:21:57,830
Today may not be the right day.

405
00:21:58,280 --> 00:21:59,590
Let's postpone it.

406
00:22:01,760 --> 00:22:03,830
I think it's a good omen.

407
00:22:04,400 --> 00:22:05,679
Our ancestors

408
00:22:05,680 --> 00:22:08,330
must have seen Sister's return,

409
00:22:08,331 --> 00:22:10,439
so they shut
the ancestral shrine's doors

410
00:22:10,440 --> 00:22:13,470
to keep our descendants
from drifting far from home.

411
00:22:14,800 --> 00:22:16,110
It's a blessing.

412
00:22:19,400 --> 00:22:20,830
Continue.

413
00:22:27,240 --> 00:22:28,150
Kneel.

414
00:22:28,400 --> 00:22:29,950
First kowtow.

415
00:22:38,240 --> 00:22:39,790
Second kowtow.

416
00:22:44,440 --> 00:22:46,270
Third kowtow.

417
00:22:52,794 --> 00:22:54,390
Offer the incense.

418
00:23:04,180 --> 00:23:08,850
(Spirit Tablet of the Late Lu Yunfei)

419
00:23:31,260 --> 00:23:34,520
♪Barging into the sea
that bears your name♪

420
00:23:34,580 --> 00:23:37,149
♪Swimming to the end with loneliness♪

421
00:23:37,150 --> 00:23:40,549
♪Going against the current
and over the reef traps♪

422
00:23:40,550 --> 00:23:43,990
♪Clearing the fog
just to get close to you♪

423
00:23:44,620 --> 00:23:47,740
♪Pushing away
the gravel hidden beneath the seaweed♪

424
00:23:47,950 --> 00:23:50,459
♪Wandering near your heart♪

425
00:23:50,460 --> 00:23:54,169
♪I imagined
our encounter countless times♪

426
00:23:54,170 --> 00:23:57,340
♪So close, yet out of reach♪

427
00:23:57,900 --> 00:24:03,400
♪Keeping
all this lonely courage to myself♪

428
00:24:04,210 --> 00:24:10,469
♪I was never part of your world♪

429
00:24:10,470 --> 00:24:14,189
♪If your silhouette
was etched upon the sea♪

430
00:24:14,190 --> 00:24:17,109
♪The sky as your wedding dress♪

431
00:24:17,110 --> 00:24:20,839
♪Turn me into a cloud♪

432
00:24:20,840 --> 00:24:23,819
♪Keep a sliver of the past♪

433
00:24:23,820 --> 00:24:27,579
♪If love is like an illusory bubble♪

434
00:24:27,580 --> 00:24:30,909
♪Together forever in my dreams♪

435
00:24:30,910 --> 00:24:36,760
♪I'd rest forever in your arms♪

436
00:24:51,260 --> 00:24:54,349
♪Barging into the sea
that bears your name♪

437
