♪Going against the current
and over the reef traps♪

439
00:25:00,540 --> 00:25:04,470
♪Clearing the fog
just to get close to you♪

440
00:25:04,620 --> 00:25:07,769
♪Returning to the land
left bare by the receding sea♪

441
00:25:07,770 --> 00:25:10,539
♪Withering like a fallen leaf♪

442
00:25:10,540 --> 00:25:14,189
♪The message in a bottle
buried on the shore♪

443
00:25:14,190 --> 00:25:17,340
♪No one asked♪

444
