♪The sky as your wedding dress♪

448
00:25:37,180 --> 00:25:40,839
♪Turn me into a cloud♪

449
00:25:40,840 --> 00:25:43,809
♪Keep a sliver of the past♪

450
00:25:43,810 --> 00:25:47,569
♪If love is like an illusory bubble♪

451
00:25:47,570 --> 00:25:50,799
♪Together forever in my dreams♪

452
00:25:50,800 --> 00:25:57,110
♪I'd rest forever in your arms♪

453
00:25:57,120 --> 00:26:00,929
♪If the sea didn't wait
for the evening breeze♪

454
00:26:00,930 --> 00:26:03,779
♪And swim with me to you♪

455
00:26:03,780 --> 00:26:07,469
♪I'd become♪

456
00:26:07,470 --> 00:26:10,469
♪A whale
who forever keeps the sea company♪

457
00:26:10,470 --> 00:26:14,189
♪If love is like a night storm♪

458
